<bibRefCitation author="GOVAERTS" box="[1020,1355,1594,1618]" etAl="&amp; al." firstAuthor="GOVAERTS" page="290" pageId="8" pageNumber="357" refId="ref11755" refString="GOVAERTS, R., M. SOBRAL, P. ASHTON, F. BARRIE, B. K. HOLST, L. L. LANDRUM, K. MATSUMOTO, F. F. MAZINE, E. N. LUGHADHA, C. PROENCA, L. H. SOARES- SILVA, P. G. WILSON &amp; E. LUCAS (2008). World checklist of Myrtaceae. Kew Publishing. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew." type="book" year="2008">GOVAERTS &amp; al. (2008: 290)</bibRefCitation>
